title: Tags operator
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The `tags` operator shows the corresponding tiddler's tags (in order of appearance in the tags field).

!! Example I
If you want to retrive the tags of [[Button Tutorial]] tiddler do as below

><$macrocall $name="wikitext-example-without-html" src="""<$list filter="[[Button Tutorial]tags[]]">
<<currentTiddler>><br>
</$list>
"""/>

!! Example II
Show the other tags for those tiddlers tagged with `kookma`

><$macrocall $name="wikitext-example-without-html" src="""<$list filter="[tag[kookma]tags[]]">
<$view field="title"/><br>
</$list>
"""/>